---
title: Chilli Garlic Hake Tagliatelle with Rocket and Olive Salad
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Chilli Garlic Hake Tagliatelle in just 10 minutes for a balanced and tasty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5f9aca31f51e756b4d128d7f-3ed657c7-10f46fd6.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chilli-garlic-hake-tagliatelle-5f9aca31f51e756b4d128d7f-bbf0244e.pdf
cuisine: Italian
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/chilli-garlic-hake-tagliatelle-5f9aca31f51e756b4d128d7f
course: main course
time required: 10 minutes
author: Mimi Morley
nutrition:
  calories: 419 kcal
